name: Mystery elf
description:
Welcome to Mystery elf: Master trainer!

It was just another day at the library when a gateway opened in a magical book left forgotten on one of the shelves. Now you’ve entered a mystery elf garden.

● Hundreds of unique plants.
● Dozens kinds of soil you can plant on.
● Harvest your plants and win extra rewards!
● Don't forget to turn the soil after the harvest.
